  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConfigurableEngine
    ConfigurableEngine extends the PIPEngine interface with methods for configuring the engine from a Properties object.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Configurables  
    EnvironmentEngine
    EnvironmentEngine implements the com.att.research.xacml.api.pip.PipEngine interface to provide values for standard environment attributes.
    RequestEngine
    StdRequestEngine implements the PIPEngine interface to retrieve matching com.att.reserach.xacml.api.Attributes from a com.att.research.xacml.pip.Request object.
    StdConfigurableEngine
    StdConfigurableEngine implements the ConfigurableEngine interface to automatically process the standard name, description, and issuer properties.
